Product details

Top highlights

  • PERFECT COMPATIBILITY - The 6000S Replacement Filter Kit is perfectly compatible with the Levoit Superior 6000s Smart Evaporative Humidifier. Please check your Levoit humidifier model carefully before purchasing
  • UPGRADED MATERIAL - The blue wick filters are made from upgraded high quality paper materials with a durable multi-layer pleated fabric structure. This maximizes water absorption, ensures the best humidity output, better extends the life of the filter and creates a comfortable home environment
  • NOTE - Suitable for all types of water, including tap water. Using filtered water can extend the life of your humidifier filter
  • WARM REMINDER - For best performance, the humidifier filter should be changed regularly. Each set of four blue filters will generally last 3-6 months, each white sponge filter will generally last 1 month, depending on water hardness
  • GREAT VALUE - Includes 16 packs of blue wick filters and 12 packs of white sponge filters. The blue wick filters can effectively trap large particles and minerals, improving the fog quality of the Superior 6000S by capturing impurities such as calcium and magnesium ions in the water to ensure the purity of the fog. The white sponge filter traps and filters fine impurities and sediments from the water, reducing water hardness
